      "originalText": "EXAMPLE\npotocal of sending package company A\n1. check product that want to send\n2. SEAL PACKAGE\n3.SEND TO DESTINATION BY COMPANY MESSENGER\n\nPOTOCAL OF SENDING PACKAGE COMPANY B\n1. CHECK PRODUCT \n2. SEND TO QA TO RECHECK\n3.SEAL PACKAGE\n4. ADD ADDRESS\n5.RECHECK ADDRESS OF SENDER\n6.RECHECK ADDRESS OF DESTINATION\n7.SEND BY MESSENGER",
